ote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efe0e46ce937cbb727b21a065506e7850f24040","tid":257644,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"-60樓都飛到"},{"pid":"c3ed970b9f224b8ee9f53cd1ac4249df934b8a61","tid":257644,"uid":21527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真住70幾樓有咩方法令佢地唔飛入嚟？</blockquote><br />\n唔開窗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經無開窗，露台好多自己甩左翼係到行"},{"pid":"2148adc8f7b456a35d922b56f0cb0c652d560e95","tid":257644,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"013daeaad8edd6deed0dbcb3989a2a56a086c893","tid":257644,"uid":9607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"細個會嘗試養佢哋，希望佢哋生到蟻仔，不過次次都失敗。"},{"pid":"7957438cb06c91d1db0d3d95303c7a6b030bd46c","tid":257644,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"我住係仙女座銀河系，一到7點就有"},{"pid":"5544ace6c6b8d3028c21b78521fbc0a18383298c","tid":257644,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個會嘗試養佢哋，希望佢哋生到蟻仔，不過次次都失敗。</blockquote><br />\n飛蟻 = 白蟻<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98cdd47c5ad2ce523edcf756c4f7e2aa8889403","tid":257644,"uid":112247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"我屋企今日都有幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07af82345bff9b999178101aa582d68e405f155c","tid":257644,"uid":43616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"負評係比低質接龍"},{"pid":"6454d5fe9f9a4c65699ab88af68716ccf0dfdc86","tid":257644,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起碼捉咗三隻，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果走甩咗一對俾佢哋交配到咪成屋白蟻？</span>點飛到咁高㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/25/200639_9f6646de10722a066bf15fb4f1a7a085.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F25%2F200639_9f6646de10722a066bf15fb4f1a7a085.jpg&h=f21bab0b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有無諗過俾頂綠帽其中一隻戴<br />\n咁佢地咪唔會交配"},{"pid":"b5fb46089fe5de4cabaf9eca6bc4650cd80ffca8","tid":257644,"uid":464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"其實平時佢地係係邊到生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e984373069ff7ebc1f53ea6b63d101da24c7a1","tid":257644,"uid":2475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:20:09.000Z","msg":"連登質素真係有眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91dfe726de9adc5bc7025f1cc7b4836e7e334cf0","tid":257644,"uid":116310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"我屋企都有！食食下飯係我頭上飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb98126e5dc22f70dd1d9656a7d302c94a65466","tid":257644,"uid":9607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個會嘗試養佢哋，希望佢哋生到蟻仔，不過次次都失敗。</blockquote><br />\n飛蟻 = 白蟻<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知，白蟻飛蟻橙色嘅，公乸差唔多樣，公會追住乸嘅尾走嚟走去，之後會掘窿交配，不過冇次有白蟻仔走出嚟，次次都係兩公婆死起個窿入面。<br />\n<br />\n有黃蟻飛蟻，亦有黑蟻飛蟻，乸大隻過公，好好打，會咬人同針人。<br />\n<br />\n我試過捉咗好多不同種類嘅黃黑飛蟻一齊起個樽仔度，最後有一隻最大嘅黑飛蟻咬死哂其他飛蟻，全部都被咬斷身體，好堅。"},{"pid":"00a2961faddad4456d81e0073f5b0c906879285e","tid":257644,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c108cfe7e6cc9a642fee244d0449ed678a95dc","tid":257644,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"低質到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd87e98ac3b12577501fa4e396c371eee38ba8f8","tid":257644,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>希望設立關愛座<br />\n飛蟻優先飛到老友記屋企</blockquote><br />\nUp Mud Lun Yea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成堆垃圾講狗話</blockquote><br />\n好撚高尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d9e4feb62f7695be249eee1f4e92cdbb03380c","tid":257644,"uid":72704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"啲接龍做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee62a8c37e6f7f0d4663871d6742bc7d58f72d0","tid":257644,"uid":20349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細個會嘗試養佢哋，希望佢哋生到蟻仔，不過次次都失敗。</blockquote><br />\n飛蟻 = 白蟻<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知，白蟻飛蟻橙色嘅，公乸差唔多樣，公會追住乸嘅尾走嚟走去，之後會掘窿交配，不過冇次有白蟻仔走出嚟，次次都係兩公婆死起個窿入面。<br />\n<br />\n有黃蟻飛蟻，亦有黑蟻飛蟻，乸大隻過公，好好打，會咬人同針人。<br />\n<br />\n我試過捉咗好多不同種類嘅黃黑飛蟻一齊起個樽仔度，最後有一隻最大嘅黑飛蟻咬死哂其他飛蟻，全部都被咬斷身體，好堅。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主係咪想練蠱毒"},{"pid":"1db2a4491efe5de4ac12602ceac98cc796565b0b","tid":257644,"uid":104748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T13:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屋企都有，不過10點幾先有，<br />\n之後狗衝入房開冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好奇怪，第二朝超身就唔見曬，一兩隻屍體都無<br />\n<br />\n不過我記得，打風前夕同之後仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal